Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:11.93,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}頑な心のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:15.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石ころはどこまで行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:18.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}砂のように脆く崩れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:22.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一文字も読めない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:24.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:28.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}ただ前に進むだけじゃ見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:38.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}言葉の出来ないものを下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:41.78,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一粒の冷たい石に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:45.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}秘められた熱もあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}どうせなら 勝ちに行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}何もかも見えない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:58.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空っぽのままの心でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:00.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:04.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}閉ざされた夢を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:08.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}勢い任せで掴んだ手が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}きっと君を変えてくsignal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}会いたくて 飛んだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:18.16,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}堕ちてゆくけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}もう一度 空を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.80,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}放り投げる想いすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}泣いだって 分け合って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}君が笑うまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:35.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,866)}stone cold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:00:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:11.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}以一顆頑固的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:15.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石塊可以去往任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:18.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如同砂土般輕易崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:22.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}無法預知一字的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:24.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:28.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如若只是一味向前則會迷失所有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:38.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}請賜予我無法用語言形容的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:41.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一顆冰冷的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:45.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}恐怕也隱藏著炙熱的溫度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}既然已經決定 那就想要取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空無一物的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:58.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算只有一顆空洞的心也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:00.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:04.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}追尋緊閉的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:08.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}把一切交給氣勢 握緊的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}絕對能夠改變你的人生signal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如此思念你 哪怕就算飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:18.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}也終會墜落消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}再一次衝上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}抱緊所有拋下的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算哭泣 也一起承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}直到你微笑的那一天
